  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 45-6-11, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE THAT IF THE MISSISSIPPI BOARD ON LAW ENFORCEMENT STANDARDS AND TRAINING CONTEMPLATES REPRIMANDING, SUSPENDING, CANCELLING OR RECALLING THE CERTIFICATION OF A LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICER, THEN SUCH OFFICER SHALL BE ENTITLED TO DISCOVERY DURING THE HEARING PROCESS OF THE BOARD; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
